    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The 12pc Universal Diamond Burr Set is the ideal accessory for your Dremel or handheld rotary tool! Each set comes with 12 high quality diamond round ball heads in assorted sizes. These burrs can be used for medium material removal by carving, etching, grinding and sanding. Each burr features a 1/8&quot; shank, and comes in a sturdy compact case for easy transportation and storage while not in use. These are great for working with ceramics, stone, glass, tile, wood, fiberglass, all natural materials and more!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Universal Tool Assorted Diamond Burr Set 120-150 Grit .125 Inch Shank (Multiple</h2>\n  <p>The 12pc Universal Diamond Burr Set is the ideal accessory for your Dremel or handheld rotary tool! Each set comes with 12 high quality diamond round ball heads in assorted sizes. These burrs can be used for medium material removal by carving, etching, grinding and sanding.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>High Quality Diamond Round Ball Heads (Assorted Sizes)</li>\n    <li><strong>Shank Size:</strong> 1/8&quot; | Grit: 150</li>\n    <li>Comes In Sturdy Compact Case</li>\n    <li>Ideal for Medium Material Removal by Carving, Etching, Grinding, Sanding, etc.</li>\n    <li>Great for Working with Ceramics, Stone, Glass, Tile, Wood, Fiberglass, All Natural Materials and More</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/Hobby_Tools/12pcDiamondBurrSet.jpg\" alt=\"The 12pc Universal Diamond Burr Set is the ideal accessory for your Dremel or handheld rotary tool\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 12DBS-1</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 772366125917</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Silver</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Each burr features a 1/8&quot; shank, and comes in a sturdy compact case for easy transportation and storage while not in use. These are great for working with ceramics, stone, glass, tile, wood, fiberglass, all natural materials and more!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The 12pc Universal Diamond Burr Set is the ideal accessory for your Dremel or handheld rotary tool! Each set comes with 12 high quality diamond round ball heads in assorted sizes. These burrs can be used for medium material removal by carving, etching, grinding and sanding. Each burr features a 1/8\" shank, and comes in a sturdy compact case for easy transportation and storage while not in use. These are great for working with ceramics, stone, glass, tile, wood, fiberglass, all natural materials and more!.",
